Bug1:
How to fix docker: Got permission denied while trying to connect to the Docker daemon socket at unix:///var/run/docker.sock: Get http://%2Fvar%2Frun%2Fdocker.sock/v1.40/containers/json: dial unix /var/run/docker.sock: connect: permission denied
Solution:
just open terminal and type this command
sudo chmod 666 /var/run/docker.sock

